<div style="padding: 20px;">
<h2>Downloading "<span style="text-transform: capitalize;">{{title}}</span>"</h2>

For direct download, click on either the <a href="/download/transfer/playlist/{{id}}/0"><button class="btn">MP3</button></a> or
    <a href="/download/transfer/playlist/{{id}}/1"><button class="btn">AIFF</button></a> download links.<br><br>

<form method="post" action="/download/playlist/{{id}}">
    For an e-mailed link, please choose the format for the download:<br>

    <input type="radio" name="format" value="0" checked="checked"> MP3<br>
    <input type="radio" name="format" value="1"> AIFF<br><br>

    Please enter the e-mail address to which you want to send the download link:<br><br>

    <input type="hidden" name="playlistid" value="{{id}}">
    <input type="text" name="target" value="{{target}}"><br><br>

    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send download info</button>
</form>

</div>
